  m_text: "Before Your Child Uses cARd AI\n\nThis app should be used with adult supervision.
    By continuing, you confirm you are the child's\nparent, legal guardian, or an
    authorized therapist/educator, and you\nagree on behalf of both yourself and
    the child.\n\nCAMERA: Used only to scan physical vocabulary cards in real time.\nNothing
    is recorded or saved from the camera.\n\nMICROPHONE: Used only if you choose
    to record your own voice for a\ncard (\"My Voice\"). Recordings are stored on
    this device only \u2014 never\nuploaded or shared.\n\nNo personal information
    is collected, sold, shared, or used for advertising from this app.\n\nNOT A MEDICAL
    DEVICE: cARd AI is a vocabulary-learning tool. It does not diagnose, treat, or
    replace professional speech, occupational, or\nbehavioral therapy.\n\nFull Terms
    & Privacy Policy: synaptic.framer.ai/legal"
